                           <p>Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 24;
                                                  written lines: 24; Uniform layout. Jonah, Zephaniah, Haggai and Malachi open a new column, and Hosea commences a new leaf.The beginning and the end of the Haftarot indicated in the margin, for the most part in red ink.Masorah magna in one to three lines in the lower margin of each page.The number of verses stated at the end of each book.</p>
